Every quadrangle S4------S3
                 |       |
                 S1------S2
of the surface mesh is cut into 2 triangles as the option 
1: S1-S2-S3   and   S1-S3-S4
2: S1-S2-S4   and   S2-S3-S4
3: the greatest angle of the future cut quadrangle
4: the maximum of minimum of 2 triangle qualities
(4 is the best choice to improve the mesh quality)

Example:
S31_TRIANGULATION;  I;  31;  QUADRANGULATION;  4;
